OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a dry and bright start,
OL,6,Fthere will be a mixture of sunny
OL,7,Fspells and showers into the afternoon,
OL,8,Flocally heavy, with the risk of hail
OL,9,Fand thunder in places. Feeling
OL,10,Fpleasant in the sunshine. Windy,
OL,11,Fespecially near the showers.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny daytime showers will
OL,14,Fgradually ease to leave a dry night,
OL,15,Fwith prolonged clear spells. Winds
OL,16,Feasing, and turning locally chilly,
OL,17,Fwith a patchy frost forming in prone
OL,18,Frural spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
